<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="/css/style.css">
    <title>Pearl Vault</title>
</head>
<body>
    <%- include('navbar') %>
    <h1>Pearl Vault</h1>
    <h3>Browse through the catalogue and discover the beauty of handcrafted pearls from Bahrain's finest local designers.</h3>
    <a href="/jewelry">Explore Jewelry</a>
    <section>
        <h4>About Pearl Vault</h4>
        <p>Inspired by the rich pearling history of our island, this platform brings Bahrain's local jewelry brands together in a single space where designers can share their work and visitors can find unique pearl pieces.</p>
    </section>

    <% if(!user) {%>
        <section>
            <h4>For Designers</h4>
            <p>Are you a local brand or designer? Create an account to list your jewelry pieces in our catalogue.</p>
            <a href="/auth/sign-up">Create an Account</a>
        </section>
    <% } else {%>
        <section>
        <h4>Welcome, <%= user.brandName %></h4>
        <p>You can add new pieces to the vault or manage your existing collection below.</p>
        <a href="/jewelry/new">Add New Jewelry</a>
        <a href="/jewelry">Manage My Pieces</a>
        </section>
    <% } %>
    
</body>
</html>